node.text:
🎙 “We had an objective, a target: to renew the team. Young players, young talent with big potential.”

We sat down with Fabio Paratici to discuss this summer’s transfer window and his first months at the club. 🎥 ⤵️

node.title: Fabio Paratici on our summer transfer window!

node.text: 🗣 "We can't get too down, we've had a good start with three wins but we'll definitely take the lessons from the result... We'll be looking to put it right on Thursday."

node.text: 🗣 “We showed resilience when we were a man down - putting bodies in front of the ball - but then came the penalty. But we didn't create enough, we didn't have the ball enough and we made mistakes."
